{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778432319616,"sessionID":"ses_1ed33e673ffe271KLA41UUqved","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_xAPgBK4RAbwaGc9vOSNjEx6v","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: DESIGN_PATTERNS.md\n+# Design Pattern Notes for Issue 31601\n+\n+Task: update textual definitions for `GO:0140597` protein carrier activity and `GO:0140309` unfolded protein holdase activity.\n+\n+No dedicated DOSDP YAML pattern was found for protein carrier/holdase activity. Existing ontology precedent was therefore used.\n+\n+Relevant precedent:\n+\n+- `GO:0140104` molecular carrier activity: \"Directly binding to a specific ion or molecule and delivering it either to an acceptor molecule or to a specific location.\"\n+- `GO:0140597` protein carrier activity has logical definition `intersection_of: GO:0140104` and `intersection_of: has_primary_input PR:000000001`, so the textual definition should mirror the parent carrier wording while substituting protein as cargo.\n+- `GO:0140309` unfolded protein holdase activity is asserted as a child of `GO:0140597`; its definition should remain a protein carrier activity definition, with the unfolded-state and aggregation-prevention specificity retained.\n+\n+Decision:\n+\n+- Do not add or alter logical definitions.\n+- Update text only, aligning `GO:0140597` with the parent carrier definition and updating `GO:0140309` to remain consistent with that revised wording.\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA DESIGN_PATTERNS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/DESIGN_PATTERNS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/DESIGN_PATTERNS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/DESIGN_PATTERNS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,16 @@\n+# Design Pattern Notes for Issue 31601\n+\n+Task: update textual definitions for `GO:0140597` protein carrier activity and `GO:0140309` unfolded protein holdase activity.\n+\n+No dedicated DOSDP YAML pattern was found for protein carrier/holdase activity. Existing ontology precedent was therefore used.\n+\n+Relevant precedent:\n+\n+- `GO:0140104` molecular carrier activity: \"Directly binding to a specific ion or molecule and delivering it either to an acceptor molecule or to a specific location.\"\n+- `GO:0140597` protein carrier activity has logical definition `intersection_of: GO:0140104` and `intersection_of: has_primary_input PR:000000001`, so the textual definition should mirror the parent carrier wording while substituting protein as cargo.\n+- `GO:0140309` unfolded protein holdase activity is asserted as a child of `GO:0140597`; its definition should remain a protein carrier activity definition, with the unfolded-state and aggregation-prevention specificity retained.\n+\n+Decision:\n+\n+- Do not add or alter logical definitions.\n+- Update text only, aligning `GO:0140597` with the parent carrier definition and updating `GO:0140309` to remain consistent with that revised wording.\n\n","files":[{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/DESIGN_PATTERNS.md","relativePath":"DESIGN_PATTERNS.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/DESIGN_PATTERNS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/DESIGN_PATTERNS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/DESIGN_PATTERNS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,16 @@\n+# Design Pattern Notes for Issue 31601\n+\n+Task: update textual definitions for `GO:0140597` protein carrier activity and `GO:0140309` unfolded protein holdase activity.\n+\n+No dedicated DOSDP YAML pattern was found for protein carrier/holdase activity. Existing ontology precedent was therefore used.\n+\n+Relevant precedent:\n+\n+- `GO:0140104` molecular carrier activity: \"Directly binding to a specific ion or molecule and delivering it either to an acceptor molecule or to a s